parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, especially when the vehicle surges forward suddenly while stopped or slowing down.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates suddenly without pressing the gas pedal
the vehicle surges forward while stopped or slowing down
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brake pedal feels spongy or soft.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A sticking brake pedal can cause the vehicle to take longer to stop, leading to accidents or injuries, especially when the vehicle is traveling at high speeds.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels spongy or soft
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brake pedal has to be pulled up with the left foot to begin acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Erratic brake performance can cause the vehicle to take longer to stop or accelerate unexpectedly, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels spongy or soft
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle takes longer to stop than usual
the brake pedal has to be pulled up with the left foot to begin acceleration
the vehicle accelerates suddenly without pressing the gas pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the acceleration pedal can cause the vehicle to hesitate or stop responding to acceleration, leading to loss of control, accidents, or life-threatening situations, especially in traffic or during turns.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to respond to acceleration pedal input
hesitates
or stops moving while in motion
especially during left turns; the pedal sensor error code is displayed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unusual engine revving noise and illumination of unknown warning indicators can distract the driver, leading to loss of control or accidents.
symptoms: The engine makes an unusual revving noise
unknown warning indicators illuminate and do not turn off
and the brake pedal stiffens
making it difficult to make a complete stop.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Tire Failure due to Manufacturing Defect
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden failure of a tire can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and potentially serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: Tire blowout
tire sidewall crumbling
loss of air pressure
tire failure at high speeds
tire failure without warning.
